nomicUtilization , dtm-business:AccessFee , dtm-data:Architecture , owl:Thing , owl:Nothing , dtm-data:DataLifecycleStage , dtm-core:Data , dtm-business:PayModel , dtm-data:ProcessingTechnique , dtm-data:ForwardingTechnique , dtm-core:DataProvider , dtm-core:Actor , dtm-misc:Properties , dtm-business:UsageGoalOfUser , dtm-data:QualityTechnique , rdfs:Resource , dtm-business:DataTrusteeGoal;
